# UX copy

When the task involves **writing, reviewing, or refining user-facing copy** (labels, errors, empty states, CTAs, confirmations, tooltips, onboarding, loading copy, microcopy), read `.agents/skills/ux-copy/SKILL.md` at the start of the task and follow its principles and output format before delivering final copy.
